parameters: Ussu.... Thank you for playing the Pre-release Demo!

You won't be able to transfer data to the full version, but we
plan to include data with the same progress as after clearing the
pre-release demo. It's a shame that it won't be the exact same
data though...

If you go straight, the playtime is about 2 hours. If you talk to
everyone in town, it's about 3 hours...? Sorry for the long
playtime for a demo version...

Speaking of which, I wonder if I was able to express a little bit
of the story I wanted to create about Vita, the blue one...?
That's the feeling I get! So, I would be happy if you could play
until that point...

Oh, right, I should appeal to the players like this while I can.
Look, smile, smile.

Oh... you have a nice smile. The players are also commenting that
you're cute, I think. (Come on, quickly comment cute!)

...What's with that face? Are you getting carried away...? Tch...
Fine, you can go home now.

S-Sorry. The introduction got a bit long... Let's start the story
right away!
